She
followed
the
steps
of
the
night,
on
its
pathway
of
stars,
far
into
the
"wee
sma'
hours
ayont
the
twal'."
She
was
with
Moore,
in
spirit,
the
whole
time;
she
was
at
his
side;
she
heard
his
voice;
she
gave
her
hand
into
his
hand;
it
rested
warm
in
